1) Request container list[Managed/unmanaged,     ok/stopped/restarting + packet loss %]

       a) send a flag for each update
       
       b) receive a request to get the list of containers
       c) reply with the list of updates
       
2) Add/Remove Container
       a) receive a request to add or remove a container + container name
       b) reply with a response status [OK/ERROR]
       
3) Set Threshold
       a) receive a request to set the threshold + threshold
       b) reply with a response status [OK/ERROR]              
